<ul class="show_items">
<li><a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/2014/WD-streams-api-20141023/">Streams API</a>. WHATWG Streams API spec provides an API for representing and handling a stream of data in JavaScript. This W3C spec is intended to extend the WHATWG spec to meet requirements specific to the browser environment.</li>
